MarkdownBlockBase.code_block: PS C:\> Get-Command -Module AzureResourceManager | Get-Help | Format-Table Name, Synopsis

Name Synopsis ---- -------- Add-AlertRule Adds or updates an alert rule of either metric, event, o... Add-AzureAccount Adds the Azure account to Windows PowerShell Add-AzureEnvironment Creates an Azure environment Add-AzureKeyVaultKey Creates a key in a vault or imports a key into a vault. ...
Get-AzureLocation | Where-Object Name -eq "ResourceGroup" | Format-Table Name, LocationsString -Wrap
Name LocationsString ---- --------------- ResourceGroup East Asia, South East Asia, East US, West US, North Central US, South Central US, Central US, North Europe, West Europe
